{"type":"message","id":"ca063539","parentId":"ebfa05f6","timestamp":"2026-03-24T06:29:46.852Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jao0obznjqdj_2","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5490\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3483\n[file inferred from ACTION] tic/tic_classifier.py\n[mutation proposed] tic/tic_classifier.py\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 022914 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next concrete step for Phase 1 advancement. I need to implement a classifier that identifies invariant vs variant content across pulse logs and tests prediction accuracy against the success criteria (>70% classification, >60% prediction).\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"wild-slug","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5490\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3483\n[file inferred from ACTION] tic/tic_classifier.py\n[mutation proposed] tic/tic_classifier.py\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 022914 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next concrete step for Phase 1 advancement. I need to implement a classifier that identifies invariant vs variant content across pulse logs and tests prediction accuracy against the success criteria (>70% classification, >60% prediction).\n","name":"powershell C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774333786851}}
